== Описание ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The '''TechDraw ExtensionArcLengthAnnotation''' tool calculates the arc length of selected edges and inserts an arc length annotation.
</div>

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionArcLengthAnnotationExample.png|480px]]
<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
{{Caption|The calculated length of a B-spline approximation of sin(x) from 0 to 2π}}
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Usage==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# Select one or more edges.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionArcLengthAnnotation.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionArcLengthAnnotation|Calculate the arc length of selected edges]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Attributes/Modifications → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionArcLengthAnnotation.svg|16px]] Calculate the arc length of selected edges}} option from the menu.
# The total arc length of the edges is calculated and an annotation is inserted.
</div>


